              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Three plutonium fission samples were used. The weights",
                "of the foils were obtained from a measured alpha",
                "emission rate, the alpha half-lives of the isotopes,",
                "and mass spectrometric determinations of the isotopic",
                "contents of the samples.",
                "   Sample   Foil Weight",
                "     1.    0.4349 mg +-1%",
                "     2.    0.428  mg +-1.5%",
                "     3.    0.9467 mg +-1.6%",
                "            Isotopic contents",
                " Isotope    Sample 1       Sample 2      Sample3",
                " 238Pu                 0.00234        0.00274+-0.00008",
                " 239Pu 0.1198+-0.0010  0.3003+-0.003  0.0604+-0.002",
                " 240Pu 0.8746+-0.0010  0.5075+-0.005  0.3914+-0.004",
                " 241Pu 0.0051+-0.00005 0.1058+-0.001  0.1924+-0.003",
                " 251Am    0.00028        0.0008          0.0062",
                " 242Pu 0.00024+-0.00001 0.0625+-0.0005 0.3468+-0.004"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
