              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The three values of each cross section were",
                " weighted by the reciprocal squares of their",
                " uncertainties and a weighted average obtained. Since",
                " the assigned uncertainties of each value were",
                " determined primarily by the uncertainties in the",
                " isotopic contents and alpha half-lives these",
                " uncertainties are not independent. The uncertainty",
                " of the final answer was then chosen as the smallest",
                " uncertainty of the individual determinations."
